com.cube.storm.ui.quiz.lib.factory

Class QuizIntentFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cube.storm.ui.lib.factory.IntentFactory
      • com.cube.storm.ui.quiz.lib.factory.QuizIntentFactory

  • public class QuizIntentFactory
extends IntentFactory
    Delegate intent factory used to inject quiz functionality into ui settings module.

    This module overrides the standard UiSettings intent factory and adds small additional functionality to handle quiz classes. The original IntentFactory is retained to allow hierarchy completion.
